Subject: [PATCH] drm/amdgpu: fix amdgpu_coredump
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 8d1a13816e59254bd3b18f5ae0895230922bd120
